{"tid":1209715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方再發新聞稿用上「暴動」一詞　譴責示威者暴力行為","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:14:49.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df50d9f9f47bc797d927acc250671abac10f19e7","tid":1209715,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"警方再發新聞稿用上「暴動」一詞 譴責示威者暴力行為<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰下午4時許表示，金鐘已進入騷亂情況。警方下午5時許發出新聞稿，在標題用上「暴動」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n新聞稿重申警方嚴厲譴責示威人士暴力行為，絕不容許破壞公共秩序和公共安全，會果斷執法，又說現時在金鐘及中區一帶的示威人士應立即停止衝擊警方防線，並盡快離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462425_1_20190612193523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462425_1_20190612193523.jpg&h=a92a827d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"231a127b3df36c3eff1aba6ec79ea0cc6ce5060f","tid":1209715,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462425-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462425-20190612.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIn4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=d278a305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462425-20190612.htm&h=57270ef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462425-20190612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"18ce33eb94df0f9c26116f6b27853849b8860334","tid":1209715,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"又暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b8d14613c58131914421060ac1084ef3c32d7e","tid":1209715,"uid":10313,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"拍手嚇親啲狗仔"},{"pid":"d42100ce7bbc81bd5673990686cec16ec267be90","tid":120971